Ngokwesitatimende esithunyelwe, ungqongqoshe uthi akumele izingane zingayi esikoleni ngenxa yokungabi nezicathulo ezifanele. Umkhankaso uzoqala eNdwedwe eJohn Makhathini Civic Centre ngo-9 ekuseni lapho azonikela khona ngezicathulo ezikoleni ezihlukene endaweni. Uzobe eseya konikezela ngezicathulo lapho akhula khona KwaMashu, ezikoleni okubalwa kuzo afunda kuzona iDukemini Primary School neSibonelo High School. Kulindeleke ukuthi izingane ezizohlomula emkhankasweni zibe ngaphezulu kuka 500.